import React from 'react'
import { Grid } from '@mui/material'

const AboutUs = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
                <Grid container spacing={2}>
                    <Grid xs={8}>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid xs={4}>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid xs={4}>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid xs={8}>
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </Box>
        </>
    )
}

export default AboutUs
